ine große Vielfalt lyrischer Formen.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 16. Mai 2019) 4aAllegorese. 4aBukolik. 4aEmblematik. 4aGelegenheitsdichtung. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh1 aLaufhütte, Hartmut.1 aSchuster, Ralf, eeditor.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2017z9783110548198oZDB-23-DKU08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2018z9783110603187oZDB-23-DKU0 cprintz978311046679940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110467000423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110467000.jpg  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DKUb2017  aZDB-23-DKUb2018